  abstract  = {The Catalogue of Somatic Mutations in Cancer (COSMIC) Cancer Gene
              Census (CGC) is an expert-curated description of the genes
              driving human cancer that is used as a standard in cancer
              genetics across basic research, medical reporting and
              pharmaceutical development. After a major expansion and complete
